<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy – noFlake" %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-cta mb-2">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. What We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly when creating an account or using the platform:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Merchants:</strong> email address, Stripe account ID</li>
        <li><strong>Clients:</strong> email address (provided by Stripe after payment)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-2">We do not collect or store payment card details — all payment information is handled directly by Stripe.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li>Operate and provide the noFlake platform</li>
        <li>Process and track hold payments</li>
        <li>Send transactional emails related to your account</li>
        <li>Respond to support requests</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-2">We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Stripe</h2>
      <p>Payments on noFlake are processed by Stripe. When you pay a hold or connect a Stripe account, you interact directly with Stripe's services. Stripe's collection and use of your information is governed by <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-cta hover:underline">Stripe's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your account information for as long as your account is active. Payment records are retained for at least 7 years to comply with financial recordkeeping requirements. You may request deletion of your account by contacting us — note that we may retain certain records as required by law.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use session cookies necessary to operate the platform (authentication). We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">6. Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable technical measures to protect your information. However, no internet transmission is completely secure. Use the platform at your own risk.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">7. Children</h2>
      <p>noFlake is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will update the "Last updated" date above when changes are made. Continued use of the platform constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">9. Contact</h2>
      <p>Privacy questions or data requests? Email us at <a href="mailto:tyler.riehl16@gmail.com" class="text-cta hover:underline">tyler.riehl16@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>
